---
description: Before controller redeploy, require commit and push in current repository.
alwaysApply: true
---

- Controller redeploy gate (MUST):
  - Before redeploying the controller, create a git commit with the required changes.
  - Commit message MUST be minimal plain text, without any additional tags/trailers/labels.
  - Before redeploying the controller, push the commit to the remote of the current repository.
  - Do NOT proceed with controller redeploy if commit or push has not been completed.
